<p>
  Phil. 3:14 (in <hi xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" rend="italics">KJ</hi> Phil. 3:13).</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="5" xml:id="note-t-5">
                            

<p>Cf. 2 Cor. 5:17.</p>
                        </note>
                        
                    
                        <note n="6" xml:id="note-t-6">
                            

<p>
